349
00:53:42,410 --> 00:53:43,660
又怎样?
{\ren}So?

350
00:53:43,740 --> 00:53:46,000
他们可能会撤退
{\ren}I think maybe they're pulling out.

351
00:53:49,330 --> 00:53:51,710
也许该去告诉连长
{\ren}Maybe somebody ought to go tell the captain.

352
00:53:51,790 --> 00:53:53,340
你想去吗?
{\ren}You wanna be the one to do it?

353
00:53:59,220 --> 00:54:01,800
我命令你别乱动
{\ren}You just stay put! I'm ordering you!

354
00:54:24,910 --> 00:54:26,370
趴低
{\ren}Down!

355
00:54:35,050 --> 00:54:37,130
趴低点
{\ren}Stay low.

356
00:55:03,700 --> 00:55:05,780
冲! 冲!
{\ren}Go! Go!

357
00:55:05,990 --> 00:55:08,080
冲! 冲!
{\ren}Go! Go!

358
00:55:48,910 --> 00:55:51,000
现在怎么办?
{\ren}What do we do now?

359
00:55:51,080 --> 00:55:55,250
在这儿等 也许会有人来支援
{\ren}We wait right here. Maybe they'll send us up some reinforcements.

360
00:55:55,330 --> 00:55:56,790
做什么?
{\ren}To do what?

361
00:55:56,880 --> 00:55:59,920
攻下敌军的据点呀
{\ren}To capture some of these fucking positions around here!

362
00:56:00,010 --> 00:56:05,470
- 你要继续进攻? - 不知道 不能直接进攻山头
{\ren}- You mean you really wanna go on with this? - Hell, no. No, not no uphill charge.

363
00:56:05,550 --> 00:56:09,220
不过如果有支援
{\ren}If they send us reinforcements, maybe we could scout around

364
00:56:09,310 --> 00:56:11,390
就能试着除掉机关枪
{\ren}and locate these machine guns.

365
00:56:11,470 --> 00:56:15,480
- 总比冒死退回去好 - 有人来了
{\ren}- Anyway, it's better than going back down. - Something's coming!

366
00:56:15,560 --> 00:56:17,480
他们来了!
{\ren}They're coming!

367
00:56:22,990 --> 00:56:24,240
他们在干什么?
{\ren}What are they doin'?

368
00:56:24,320 --> 00:56:27,410
他们为什么不全力进攻?
{\ren}If they want to throw us out, why didn't they come in force?

369
00:56:27,490 --> 00:56:29,700
也许他们落了单
{\ren}Maybe they was acting on their own.

370
00:56:31,200 --> 00:56:33,710
也许他们想上西天
{\ren}Maybe they wanted to get into nirvana.

371
00:56:35,210 --> 00:56:37,080
敌人来了
{\ren}They're coming.

372
00:56:47,140 --> 00:56:48,300
怎么回事?
{\ren}Keck!

373
00:56:48,390 --> 00:56:49,800
天啊
{\ren}Jesus!

374
00:56:49,890 --> 00:56:51,970
老天!
{\ren}Oh, Jesus!

375
00:56:53,600 --> 00:56:55,230
我炸到屁股!
{\ren}I blew my butt off!

376
00:56:55,310 --> 00:56:58,730
- 没事 没事 - 我把屁股炸掉了
{\ren}- It's all right. It's all right. - I blew my butt off!

377
00:56:58,810 --> 00:57:00,270
趴下来
{\ren}Lay down!

378
00:57:00,360 --> 00:57:03,110
我怎么会这么衰?
{\ren}What a fucking recruit trick to pull!

379
00:57:03,190 --> 00:57:06,200
- 我只拔到保险制 - 写信给我老婆
{\ren}- Take it easy. Take it easy. - I grabbed it by the pin!

380
00:57:06,910 --> 00:57:11,330
告诉她我死得很光荣
